---
title: Hearty Beef Stew Over Barley with Peas and Root Veggies
description: Beef stew and barley is kind of like the food equivalent of a well-worn, fuzzy sweater. As soon as you put it on (or taste your first spoonful), you’re transported to a comfy place where everything feels familiar and warm. Which is why we’re digging it out of our proverbial recipe closet: between the savory beef cubes, tender root veggies, and hearty stew spices, it’s a timeless dish that never goes out of fashion.
